des:
Alexa and Danfoss Ally products works together to make control of your home heating easy and convenient.

Connect Alexa to your Danfoss Ally products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download the "Danfoss Ally" app from Google Play or iOS app store;
(2). Register a Danfoss Ally account in our "Danfoss Ally" app;
(3). Make sure that you have a Danfoss Ally eTRV available;
(5). Setup your Danfoss Ally eTRV using the Danfoss Ally app;
(6). Download Amazon ""Alexa"" app from Google play,iOS or Amazon app market;
(7). Configure Echo with ""Alexa"" app;
(8). Search "Danfoss Ally" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(9). Click Enable skill of "Danfoss Ally", and you'll be navigated to Danfoss Ally login page;
(10). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(11). Setup is now complete. 

You can now use voice control for controlling your heatig devices like these:
“Alexa, what is the temperature of the heater ?"
“Alexa, set the temperature of the heater to 20 degrees"
“Alexa, please raise the temperature of the heater to 22 degrees"
